Fort Myers is known for...
Spring Training for both the
Boston Red Sox
and
Minnesota Twins
.
Beautiful weather with winter temps in low 80's during the day and low 60's at night.
Legendary beaches and nearby islands such as
Sanibel
,
Captiva,
Fort Myers Beach
and
Pine
Island
.
Gorgeous sunsets from a beach, boat or backyard. Your experience is sure to be remarkable! Watch for the "
green flash
," a seaside phenomenon.
The outdoor lifestyle. From fishing to tennis to pickleball to paddle boards to shelling - there is something for everyone!
​
Visit 10 Best
for the top 10 things to do in  Fort Myers.
